Subject FW in A et al Attached is a draft order circulated late this afternoon The intent of the Commission is to vote on it at Thursdays meeting The order implements the provision in AB x to suspend direct access We are given hours to comment In addition note ordering paragraph six which gives parties days to address how the Commission should implement the suspension of direct access If you want to lob comments in tomorrow please call me first thing in the morning I must leave for hearings at the Commission at CPUCvAetalDeUlloaAgendaDecdoc Jeanne Bennett CPUCvAetalDeUlloaAgendaDecdoc
